    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;illusion&nbsp;(glamer);\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;bard 3, cleric/oracle 5, inquisitor 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, DF<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;any number of creatures in a 30-ft.-radius burst<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level (D)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>All targets are rendered silent, as per <i>silence</i>. The <i>silence</i> affects the entirety of each creature but does not extend beyond. However, the <i>silence</i> is one-way-sounds from outside the creatures' spaces can still enter. Quieted creatures gain a +10 circumstance bonus on Stealth checks.</p>\n</div>\n",
